{"tid":2513103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：飲水也屬国安範疇","createTime":"2021-05-02T08:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T09:48:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"140f942e8d9968f0bce0712c682b8cdc62ee7d43","tid":2513103,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄撰文稱，學校是教育的地方，應讓學生明白到，香港既得到國家的大力支持，亦肩負愛護國家及維護國家安全的責任，稱國家安全教育不限於認識《國安法】，更重要是讓學生明白國家安全涉及不同領域，包括國土安全、經濟安全、文化安全、社會安全、生態安全、網絡安全、科技安全等十多個範疇，與日常生活息息相關。他指，十分認聖公會聖雅各小學校長在國家安全日活動上的講話，指國家安全範疇廣泛，大如國防和軍事安全，小至飲用水的安全、日常生活中的網絡安全，也是十分重要，「因此，國家安全不只是成年人的事情，學生也應該從小開始，逐一認識國家安全的概念，日後為國家、為香港作出貢獻。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210502/465555188376145920987241.png/1qyqTgIJ4zAEoxX_OIIP7qRCBQdbKsMgEiCSbBIgkmw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210502%2F465555188376145920987241.png%2F1qyqTgIJ4zAEoxX_OIIP7qRCBQdbKsMgEiCSbBIgkmw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=ddbbd8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01. com/政情/6198 68/</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d965106846d60b2296a3c1f0a91438daeb884064","tid":2513103,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"局長你個仔都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcybSVWU8AA3Cwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEcybSVWU8AA3Cwh.jpg&h=6a023fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.asia/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/WhatsApp-Image-2021-04-06-at-11.57.42-PM.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-04-06-at-11.57.42-PM.jpeg&h=381bf986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1ef0c8b2f0042ed4705529a005618a427c1d10b","tid":2513103,"uid":357031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀，所以香港應該盡快仿效以色列，興建現代化海水化淡廠，以防有恐怖分子在東江供水系統落毒，影響香港的食水安全 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e83bc89e4770de6c2e3ba62e119f2df638c698e","tid":2513103,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"包括國土安全、經濟安全、文化安全、社會安全、生態安全、網絡安全、科技安全等十多個範疇<br />\n<br />\n支共咁多個安全唯獨係無食品安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91429c13f07da0820f57e708fe17e53eab9c8ade","tid":2513103,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"打J算唔算 會唔會遲啲淨係迫你睇支那av<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffbfedd612d279f95c14ea5d4d292e586fb50b7","tid":2513103,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"屙屎唔出都算"},{"pid":"f2567cea004f2c344c92dbf570e7028f961cc790","tid":2513103,"uid":282210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"楊局長你個仔投奔咗澳洲，有義務效忠和保護國家。局長你同個仔脫離父子關係未？如果未，本人極度懷疑你對黨嘅絕對忠誠"},{"pid":"c25e4f6760cb81ad39ac4707f72e80898bf03797","tid":2513103,"uid":302097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91429c13f07da0820f57e708fe17e53eab9c8ade","tid":2513103,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"打J算唔算 會唔會遲啲淨係迫你睇支那av<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"睇嚟要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbceaee98812b329f3f53180fe05331e7688249","tid":2513103,"uid":302097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2567cea004f2c344c92dbf570e7028f961cc790","tid":2513103,"uid":282210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"楊局長你個仔投奔咗澳洲，有義務效忠和保護國家。局長你同個仔脫離父子關係未？如果未，本人極度懷疑你對黨嘅絕對忠誠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05